style="line-height:1.8em; font-size:16px;"><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Our nonprofit was founded to help provide financial coverage for hospice patients and their families. When thinking about the name of the organization, Healthcare in Heaven Founder, Mackenzie Dexter, knew she wanted to include "healthcare" in the title to promote the mission to provide healthcare coverage. As for the origin of "heaven", Mackenzie wanted to portray the Catholic ideals that people go to heaven after death. In a way, she wanted to provide a positive outlook on a tragic, heartbreaking situation and show that this is not the end, but the </span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="wixui-rich-text__text">beginning</span><span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&nbsp;of a new life in Heaven.&nbsp;</span></p></div><div id="comp-man8uxwz1" class="comp-man8uxwz1" data-semantic-classname="button"><a data-testid="linkElement" href="https://www.healthcareinheaven.com/about-4" target="_self" class="StylableButton2545352419__root style-man8uxx11__root wixui-button StylableButton2545352419__link" aria-label="Read More"><span class="StylableButton2545352419__container"><span class="StylableButton2545352419__label wixui-button__label" data-testid="stylablebutton-label">Read More</span><span class="StylableButton2545352419__icon wixui-button__icon" aria-hidden="true" data-testid="stylablebutton-icon"><span><svg data-bbox="19.999 58 160.001 84" viewBox="0 0 200 200" height="200" width="200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" data-type="shape">
